# ── Trained model ──
# The model binary is NOT versioned in git. It's hosted on the Hugging
# Face Hub and downloaded automatically at runtime (see app.py).
# If you keep a local copy for development, drop it in artifacts/ —
# this rule keeps it out of git.
artifacts/best_model.keras
*.keras
*.h5

